                            global ocean conservation efforts."</p>

                        <small class="text-muted">Posted on August 08, 2023</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-see-more" id="seeMoreBtn" onclick="toggleComments()">See more</button>


        </div>
        <div class="map-container ">
            <div class="map-viewport " id="mapViewport">
                <div class="map-image" id="mapImage">
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="zoom-controls">
                <button class="zoom-btn" id="zoomIn" title="Zoom In">+</button>
                <button class="zoom-btn" id="zoomOut" title="Zoom Out">−</button>
            </div>

            <div class="map-info">
                <div class="zoom-level" id="zoomLevel">Zoom: 100%</div>
                <div class="coordinates" id="coordinates">Position: (0, 0)</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>